Name: Silvermane Cannoneer
Desc: A cannoneer of the Silvermane Guards who wields a portable hand cannon into battle.\nDuring combat, Silvermane Cannoneers will launch brutal chain attacks with their allies.

SkillList.SkillDesc: Deals minor Physical DMG to a single target and units adjacent to the target.
Provides support to a friendly unit. When this unit attacks, it performs a follow-up attack that deals minor Physical DMG to the attacked target and units adjacent to the target.
